{"tid":1272033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 自己思考下啦","createTime":"2019-07-01T08:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T08:54:11.000Z","uid":244186,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11edea6d95bee08f05db276375121e1401f513b4","tid":1272033,"uid":244186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"你地知唔知自己係度做梗咩 <br />\n<br />\n警察唔會開槍驅趕 <br />\n因為我地宜家人多加上上一次佢地已經蝕底<br />\n佢地暫時係唔會做出任何既行動 <br />\n除非我地繼續衝擊 <br />\n<br />\n但係換我地衝擊既話就係我地錯 仲要錯得離譜<br />\n錯在我地宜家衝擊梗一個無人既地方<br />\n我地想表達訴求既話會唔會係衝擊佢所在既地方<br />\n好過係呢度鳩坐？ <br />\n我地宜家鳩坐左1個禮拜有咩成果？<br />\n宜家唔係分化 只不過係比更好既意見大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭月娥今晚8點會係紅館啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千奇唔好去紅館堵失佢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325e7f39830bc99302910feac9a077dab5f5ecc9","tid":1272033,"uid":247203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"你肯定林鄭去？今日已經冇公布"},{"pid":"9d18f1911345f2b5e23c48278ea0de044cabd935","tid":1272033,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"又block 多個"},{"pid":"7d560564e344196405ab4fd8c030a6e6e0c29892","tid":1272033,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36b0a9662ac560465d89b7f9d6ce490d64f8bf53","tid":1272033,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">244186</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef9b441833fd206804db551d46ba42755997f2b3","tid":1272033,"uid":244186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b0a9662ac560465d89b7f9d6ce490d64f8bf53","tid":1272033,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"